<van-list
    
    v-model="loading"
    :finished="finished"
    finished-text="没有更多了"
    @load="onLoad"
    >
    <van-cell 
    v-for="item in hotList" 
     
    :key="item.id" 
    :title="item.name" 
    :label="item.copywriter"
     
    
     >
      <template #icon>
            <van-image :src="item.picUrl+'?param=200y200'" 
            :height=50 
            :width=50 
            lazy-load 
            :loading-icon="require('../assets/loading.gif')"
            style="margin:0 6px;"/>
      </template>
     </van-cell>
    
    
    </van-list>
